1
00:01:21,400 --> 00:01:22,510
Young Master Xiao,

2
00:01:22,840 --> 00:01:24,240
you finally asked me out.

3
00:01:26,400 --> 00:01:27,200
Wait.

4
00:01:27,789 --> 00:01:29,510
Should I call you Xiao Qi

5
00:01:29,789 --> 00:01:30,920
or Tang Qi?

6
00:01:34,640 --> 00:01:35,229
Up to you.

7
00:01:36,590 --> 00:01:38,450
Then, I'll still call you Xiao Qi.

8
00:01:42,759 --> 00:01:45,200
I’m still half asleep now.

9
00:01:45,280 --> 00:01:46,870
No, this doesn't count.

10
00:01:47,590 --> 00:01:49,720
You'd go to the bar with me another day.

11
00:01:50,070 --> 00:01:52,530
I have serious business
to discuss with you.

12
00:01:52,950 --> 00:01:54,150
You need my help, huh?

13
00:01:55,070 --> 00:01:57,000
Then, you have to promise me first.

14
00:01:57,509 --> 00:01:58,200
Okay.

15
00:01:58,840 --> 00:01:59,870
I promise you.

16
00:02:00,760 --> 00:02:02,400
As long as you help me get this done,

17
00:02:02,400 --> 00:02:03,860
I'll go to the bar with you.

18
00:02:09,400 --> 00:02:10,240
Deal.

19
00:02:13,910 --> 00:02:15,710
I didn't expect you to come.

20
00:02:17,750 --> 00:02:18,950
Thank you for coming.

21
00:02:22,800 --> 00:02:24,150
How's business been?

22
00:02:24,150 --> 00:02:25,190
Pretty good.

23
00:02:30,560 --> 00:02:31,800
We've made a bargain,

24
00:02:32,280 --> 00:02:33,840
and the money has been received.

25
00:02:33,840 --> 00:02:35,040
That guy is upstairs.

26
00:02:37,310 --> 00:02:38,110
Take me to him.

27
00:03:11,840 --> 00:03:12,840
Let's head over.

28
00:03:16,840 --> 00:03:17,630
Jian Xi.

29
00:03:17,870 --> 00:03:19,930
Long time no see! I missed you so much.

30
00:03:20,079 --> 00:03:21,150
Didn't you go abroad?

31
00:03:21,150 --> 00:03:22,120
Why are you back?

32
00:03:22,960 --> 00:03:24,560
It's so boring abroad.

33
00:03:24,750 --> 00:03:25,960
I missed my ‌bestie‌s here,

34
00:03:25,960 --> 00:03:26,840
so I came back.

35
00:03:28,840 --> 00:03:31,079
I heard that
you and Lu Fan aren't married yet.

36
00:03:31,079 --> 00:03:32,010
What's going on?

37
00:03:33,400 --> 00:03:35,130
It's all because of that bitch.

38
00:03:37,150 --> 00:03:38,190
No way.

39
00:03:38,560 --> 00:03:40,630
After what happened between
them three years ago,

40
00:03:40,630 --> 00:03:41,030
they still…

41
00:03:41,030 --> 00:03:42,470
It's not what you think.

42
00:03:43,630 --> 00:03:44,590
Alright.

43
00:03:44,630 --> 00:03:45,710
Anyway,

44
00:03:45,800 --> 00:03:46,600
I support you.

45
00:03:48,710 --> 00:03:50,079
Let me introduce you.

46
00:03:50,240 --> 00:03:51,560
This is Zhao Yuan.

47
00:03:52,120 --> 00:03:54,380
This is her grandpa's birthday banquet.

48
00:03:55,079 --> 00:03:56,910
You're Mr. Zhao's granddaughter.

49
00:03:56,910 --> 00:03:57,560
Hello.

50
00:03:57,560 --> 00:03:58,360
Hello.

51
00:04:00,310 --> 00:04:01,630
Jian Xi, look at Yuan's dress.

52
00:04:01,630 --> 00:04:02,680
It's pretty.

53
00:04:10,560 --> 00:04:12,430
Mr. Lu, long time no see.

54
00:04:13,030 --> 00:04:13,840
A toast to you.

55
00:04:26,190 --> 00:04:27,590
Let me toast Mr. Xiao too.

56
00:04:34,680 --> 00:04:36,270
Mr. Lu, you'd toast me.

57
00:04:36,510 --> 00:04:37,560
I just wonder

58
00:04:37,560 --> 00:04:39,040
whether you'll like

59
00:04:39,310 --> 00:04:40,770
the gift I'm giving to you.

60
00:04:41,600 --> 00:04:42,800
You brought me a gift?

61
00:04:44,600 --> 00:04:45,240
Here it is.

62
00:05:38,680 --> 00:05:41,010
Do you want to know why
I wanted to slap you?

63
00:05:41,190 --> 00:05:42,040
This slap

64
00:05:42,430 --> 00:05:45,040
is for my bestie, Jian Xi.

65
00:05:46,270 --> 00:05:47,430
You bitch

66
00:05:48,240 --> 00:05:50,920
not only harmed the Lu family
who helped you a lot,

67
00:05:50,920 --> 00:05:53,180
but also had an affair with your brother.

68
00:05:53,830 --> 00:05:55,360
Jian Xi has done so much

69
00:05:55,430 --> 00:05:57,310
for Lu Fan in the past years.

70
00:05:57,720 --> 00:05:59,450
But you still haven't given up.

71
00:05:59,680 --> 00:06:01,810
You still want to seduce your brother.

72
00:06:03,560 --> 00:06:05,750
You are a bitch.

73
00:06:06,360 --> 00:06:07,430
Ms. Zhao,

74
00:06:07,630 --> 00:06:09,680
this is a high-end banquet.

75
00:06:10,480 --> 00:06:11,800
Have you invited her?

76
00:06:12,560 --> 00:06:15,240
We can't just let

77
00:06:15,240 --> 00:06:17,680
any lowlife in.

78
00:06:19,070 --> 00:06:19,830
Wu Qing.

79
00:06:20,190 --> 00:06:22,000
I've never been against you
all these years.

80
00:06:22,000 --> 00:06:23,040
Do you know why?

81
00:06:23,600 --> 00:06:25,000
It's not because I'm afraid of you,

82
00:06:25,000 --> 00:06:26,510
but because you're beneath me.

83
00:06:26,510 --> 00:06:27,480
Besides,

84
00:06:27,600 --> 00:06:29,190
you don't really hate me.

85
00:06:29,190 --> 00:06:30,650
You're just jealous of me.

86
00:06:31,000 --> 00:06:32,920
You're actually jealous of an ant

87
00:06:32,920 --> 00:06:35,380
you've looked down on
since you were a child.

88
00:06:36,480 --> 00:06:37,430
I should know such low-class trash
like you

89
00:06:37,430 --> 00:06:39,360
can't understand decent words.

90
00:06:41,750 --> 00:06:42,560
Bitch!

91
00:06:46,680 --> 00:06:47,360
Are you okay?

92
00:06:47,360 --> 00:06:47,800
I'm fine.

93
00:06:47,800 --> 00:06:48,800
Are you hurt?

94
00:06:50,800 --> 00:06:51,560
Stop it.

95
00:06:51,600 --> 00:06:53,480
I'm helping you, Jian Xi.

96
00:06:53,680 --> 00:06:54,480
Alright.

97
00:06:57,430 --> 00:06:58,000
You...

98
00:07:03,720 --> 00:07:05,830
Today is my grandfather's
birthday banquet.

99
00:07:05,830 --> 00:07:07,390
Thank you all for coming.

100
00:07:08,120 --> 00:07:10,980
It is also the engagement party
for my bestie Jian Xi

101
00:07:11,070 --> 00:07:12,510
and Lu Fan.

102
00:07:12,830 --> 00:07:13,870
Welcome them.

103
00:07:16,040 --> 00:07:17,500
Congratulations, Mr. Lu.

104
00:07:17,800 --> 00:07:19,560
We all know that Ms. Jian and Mr. Lu

105
00:07:19,560 --> 00:07:21,160
are childhood sweethearts.

106
00:07:21,480 --> 00:07:23,720
They're a perfect match.

107
00:07:24,120 --> 00:07:25,430
When will you get married?

108
00:07:25,430 --> 00:07:26,720
We are all waiting for it.

109
00:07:26,720 --> 00:07:27,680
Yeah, when?

110
00:07:27,680 --> 00:07:28,920
Everyone is waiting for your wedding.

111
00:07:28,920 --> 00:07:30,390
You might not know this,

112
00:07:30,800 --> 00:07:33,920
Jian Xi and Lu Fan are more than
childhood sweethearts.

113
00:07:34,310 --> 00:07:35,630
When Jian Xi was young,

114
00:07:35,680 --> 00:07:37,360
she saved Lu Fan's life

115
00:07:37,510 --> 00:07:39,040
and took a knife for him.

116
00:07:40,390 --> 00:07:41,830
Mr. Lu, is this true?

117
00:07:42,950 --> 00:07:44,000
Jian Xi,

118
00:07:44,950 --> 00:07:47,159
come up and show everyone.

119
00:07:48,120 --> 00:07:48,870
Forget it.

120
00:07:49,190 --> 00:07:51,120
It happened a long time ago.

121
00:07:51,240 --> 00:07:52,630
And I believe

122
00:07:53,360 --> 00:07:55,120
Lu Fan isn't getting engaged to me

123
00:07:55,120 --> 00:07:56,850
just because I got hurt for him.

124
00:07:59,240 --> 00:08:00,040
Mr. Lu,

125
00:08:00,510 --> 00:08:02,240
be a man,

126
00:08:02,360 --> 00:08:04,000
and make yourself clear.

127
00:08:04,310 --> 00:08:07,240
Are you going to marry her or not?

128
00:08:08,430 --> 00:08:09,870
For so many years, Jian Xi

129
00:08:09,920 --> 00:08:11,560
has done so much for you.

130
00:08:12,600 --> 00:08:15,040
There are plenty of men pursuing her.

131
00:08:19,240 --> 00:08:20,360
I see.

132
00:08:21,040 --> 00:08:23,950
Someone here is making it
awkward for you, right?

133
00:08:26,120 --> 00:08:27,040
Guards,

134
00:08:27,560 --> 00:08:29,830
kick her out.

135
00:08:30,720 --> 00:08:31,750
Who dares?

136
00:08:36,630 --> 00:08:39,360
Grandpa, why did you come out now?

137
00:08:39,549 --> 00:08:41,150
I haven't acted enough yet.

138
00:08:42,720 --> 00:08:43,390
Enough.

139
00:08:47,200 --> 00:08:48,000
Bring him up.

140
00:08:58,120 --> 00:08:58,910
Jian Xi,

141
00:08:59,600 --> 00:09:00,930
do you know this person?

142
00:09:06,390 --> 00:09:07,750
You were young then,

143
00:09:08,360 --> 00:09:10,290
so you might not remember clearly.

144
00:09:10,440 --> 00:09:11,720
But your father

145
00:09:12,000 --> 00:09:13,800
will definitely recognize him.

146
00:09:15,960 --> 00:09:16,750
Lu Fan,

147
00:09:17,600 --> 00:09:20,130
the person who took the knife
for you back then

148
00:09:20,200 --> 00:09:21,120
was not Jian Xi.

149
00:09:25,200 --> 00:09:26,150
It was Su Xia.

150
00:09:33,000 --> 00:09:33,630
Lu Fan.

151
00:09:40,360 --> 00:09:41,290
Can you prove it?

152
00:10:38,440 --> 00:10:39,270
Understood?

153
00:10:39,390 --> 00:10:40,320
Don't worry.

154
00:10:42,720 --> 00:10:43,840
Jian Xi goes

155
00:10:44,320 --> 00:10:46,450
to this beauty salon every Wednesday.

156
00:10:54,390 --> 00:10:56,440
Su Xia is a bitch.

157
00:10:56,670 --> 00:10:58,240
She pesters Xiao Qi all day.

158
00:10:58,480 --> 00:10:59,960
I can't even meet him.

159
00:11:00,840 --> 00:11:02,000
Help me investigate her.

160
00:11:02,000 --> 00:11:03,150
I must stop her.

161
00:11:04,360 --> 00:11:05,150
Also,

162
00:11:05,200 --> 00:11:06,600
look into her background

163
00:11:06,720 --> 00:11:07,850
and where she lives.

164
00:11:08,390 --> 00:11:09,080
Yes.

165
00:11:14,270 --> 00:11:16,030
Okay, wait for me.

166
00:11:16,030 --> 00:11:17,360
I'll go there right now.

167
00:11:30,270 --> 00:11:31,030
Hello.

168
00:11:32,120 --> 00:11:33,180
Hello. And you are?

169
00:11:33,510 --> 00:11:34,550
I'm Jian Xi.

170
00:11:34,670 --> 00:11:37,440
Actually, I know Su Xia very well.

171
00:11:38,360 --> 00:11:39,870
Hello, I'm Zhao Yuan.

172
00:11:40,510 --> 00:11:41,390
Would you like to

173
00:11:41,390 --> 00:11:43,080
talk with me somewhere else?

174
00:11:43,240 --> 00:11:44,030
Sure.

175
00:11:50,670 --> 00:11:53,080
Su Xia is so shameless.

176
00:11:53,200 --> 00:11:54,400
She's so despicable.

177
00:11:55,000 --> 00:11:55,750
No.

178
00:11:56,120 --> 00:11:57,510
I can't let Xiao Qi

179
00:11:57,510 --> 00:11:58,630
meet her anymore.

180
00:11:59,790 --> 00:12:01,510
You don't know her.

181
00:12:02,080 --> 00:12:04,320
She is manipulative and ruthless.

182
00:12:04,670 --> 00:12:07,400
She is hard on herself, and even
harder on others.

183
00:12:08,080 --> 00:12:09,120
She is still

184
00:12:09,670 --> 00:12:11,630
pestering my fiancé.

185
00:12:17,440 --> 00:12:19,750
Based on what you just said,

186
00:12:19,840 --> 00:12:21,570
your matter seems more urgent.

187
00:12:22,390 --> 00:12:23,480
Do you have

188
00:12:23,910 --> 00:12:25,550
any way to deal with her now?

189
00:12:27,870 --> 00:12:29,480
Not yet.

190
00:12:38,510 --> 00:12:39,670
I actually have a plan

191
00:12:39,670 --> 00:12:40,670
that can help you.

192
00:12:41,240 --> 00:12:43,360
Not only will it ruin her reputation,

193
00:12:43,600 --> 00:12:45,270
but it will also let Xiao Qi

194
00:12:45,440 --> 00:12:47,000
see her true colors.

195
00:12:47,670 --> 00:12:49,530
It kills two birds with one stone.

196
00:12:49,910 --> 00:12:50,670
Really?

197
00:13:15,120 --> 00:13:15,790
Ten years.

198
00:13:21,870 --> 00:13:24,000
You have fooled me for ten whole years.

199
00:13:26,670 --> 00:13:27,510
Lu Fan.

200
00:13:28,550 --> 00:13:30,480
Don't act like a victim.

201
00:13:30,960 --> 00:13:32,200
I did lie to you.

202
00:13:33,510 --> 00:13:35,150
But for the past ten years,

203
00:13:35,240 --> 00:13:38,080
whether you were gentle
or considerate to me,

204
00:13:39,080 --> 00:13:41,280
I couldn't feel any sincerity from you.

205
00:13:44,960 --> 00:13:47,480
This is the biggest concession
I can give you

206
00:13:47,480 --> 00:13:48,720
from Jian Group.

207
00:13:50,270 --> 00:13:51,930
Take it as my repayment to you.

208
00:13:54,270 --> 00:13:55,870
Can you afford to pay it back?

209
00:14:02,910 --> 00:14:03,870
I'm telling you,

210
00:14:05,000 --> 00:14:06,600
you can't give me what I want.

211
00:14:07,200 --> 00:14:09,960
I don't need you to pay me back,
but what about Su Xia?

212
00:14:09,960 --> 00:14:11,420
What is she supposed to do?

213
00:14:13,630 --> 00:14:15,270
If she has the ability,

214
00:14:15,790 --> 00:14:17,520
she can come and get it herself.

215
00:14:25,960 --> 00:14:27,200
With no more expectations of you,

216
00:14:27,200 --> 00:14:28,840
I can handle everything,

217
00:14:29,000 --> 00:14:30,330
and I can afford to lose.

218
00:14:31,080 --> 00:14:32,140
But what about you?

219
00:14:33,390 --> 00:14:34,990
Can you still afford to lose,

220
00:14:36,200 --> 00:14:37,080
Mr. Lu?

221
00:15:18,750 --> 00:15:19,550
Mr. Xiao,

222
00:15:19,630 --> 00:15:20,480
regarding the cooperation,

223
00:15:20,480 --> 00:15:22,320
there shouldn't be a big problem
with Mr. Jian,

224
00:15:22,320 --> 00:15:24,450
but he hopes to meet with you in person.

225
00:15:50,870 --> 00:15:51,670
Dad.

226
00:15:52,670 --> 00:15:53,510
I'm sorry.

227
00:15:54,200 --> 00:15:56,860
Zhao Yuan and Su Xia definitely
knew each other.

228
00:15:56,870 --> 00:15:58,130
She is behind all this.

229
00:15:58,200 --> 00:16:00,200
What's the point of saying this now?

230
00:16:01,320 --> 00:16:02,200
Ultimately,

231
00:16:02,390 --> 00:16:04,630
you didn't win Lu Fan's heart.

232
00:16:06,840 --> 00:16:08,440
Are we just going to let it go?

233
00:16:09,440 --> 00:16:12,200
I must make Su Xia pay.

234
00:16:13,030 --> 00:16:14,600
If you could really do so,

235
00:16:14,600 --> 00:16:16,600
you wouldn't be in this situation today.

236
00:16:16,600 --> 00:16:18,330
How do you want to deal with her?

237
00:16:18,600 --> 00:16:19,750
Kidnap her again?

238
00:16:20,390 --> 00:16:21,250
Will that work?

239
00:16:22,510 --> 00:16:24,240
It's not like we haven't tried.

240
00:16:24,550 --> 00:16:25,200
Dad.

241
00:16:28,630 --> 00:16:31,030
You are the one
who kidnapped her last time?

242
00:16:34,240 --> 00:16:36,120
That doesn't matter.

243
00:16:38,320 --> 00:16:40,120
Do you think Lu Fan

244
00:16:40,630 --> 00:16:42,240
will get back at me

245
00:16:42,750 --> 00:16:44,810
and affect our cooperation project?

246
00:16:47,510 --> 00:16:49,030
My silly daughter.

247
00:16:50,000 --> 00:16:52,790
Lu Fan's revenge is because he cares.

248
00:16:52,960 --> 00:16:54,910
If Lu Fan cares about you,

249
00:16:57,030 --> 00:16:59,230
we wouldn't be in this situation today.

250
00:17:01,870 --> 00:17:04,109
We need to think of a way out.

251
00:17:04,550 --> 00:17:06,310
Our relationship with the Lu family

252
00:17:06,310 --> 00:17:07,310
is superficially

253
00:17:08,109 --> 00:17:09,069
okay right now,

254
00:17:11,480 --> 00:17:12,790
but it won't last long.

255
00:17:22,510 --> 00:17:23,069
Hello.

256
00:17:23,829 --> 00:17:26,440
Mr. Jian, I think we can talk.

257
00:17:27,270 --> 00:17:28,109
I'm Xiao Qi.

258
00:17:30,440 --> 00:17:31,550
Mr. Xiao?
